          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fairness and Opportunities for Married Households With Student Loans Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase to $5,000 the tax deduction for interest on education loans for married couples filing a joint tax return.</p>]]></text>
